- content_for :title, "Board Dimensions - Fun Stuff"

.max-w-6xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.py-8
  / Breadcrumb
  = render 'shared/breadcrumbs', breadcrumbs: [{ title: 'Home', path: '/' }, { title: 'Fun Stuff', path: fun_stuff_path }, { title: 'Board Dimensions', path: nil }]

  / Main Content Card
  .bg-white.rounded-lg.shadow-lg.overflow-hidden
    / Header Section
    = render 'shared/page_header', title: 'Board Dimensions', subtitle: 'Technical specifications and mounting information for all Baldrick boards'

    / Content Section
    .px-8.py-8
      .max-w-4xl.mx-auto
        .prose.max-w-none
          h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-6 Baldrick Dimensions

          p.text-lg.text-gray-700.mb-6
            | Baldrick Boards are categorized into two board sizes: 
            strong small
            |  and 
            strong medium
            | . This means that we don't have to keep making new mounts and accessory sizes as we create new boards.

          .bg-blue-50.border-l-4.border-blue-400.p-4.mb-8
            .flex
              .flex-shrink-0
                svg.h-5.w-5.text-blue-400 viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                  path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"
              .ml-3
                p.text-sm.text-blue-700
                  strong Important:
                  |  Mounting holes in all our boards are 
                  strong M3
                  | . Please use the correct hardware for secure mounting.

          / Small Boards
          .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6.mb-8
            h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Small Boards
            p.text-gray-700.mb-6
              | We've designed the Small boards so they can be hidden inside a small junction or project box.
            
            .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.items-center
              div
                h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Small Board Specifications
                ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                  li • 
                    strong Category:
                    |  Small form factor
                  li • 
                    strong Mounting Holes:
                    |  M3
                  li • 
                    strong Typical Use:
                    |  Junction boxes, small enclosures
                  li • 
                    strong Installation:
                    |  Hidden installations
              .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-4
                img src="/img/dimensions-small.jpeg" alt="Small Baldrick Board Dimensions" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
                p.text-sm.text-gray-600.mt-2.text-center Small Baldrick Board Dimensions

          / Medium Boards
          .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6.mb-8
            h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Medium Boards
            p.text-gray-700.mb-6
              | We based the dimensions of the 
              strong Medium Baldrick boards
              |  to match similar boards already in the market so you can reuse mounts and 3D printed elements.
            
            .bg-purple-50.border-l-4.border-purple-400.p-4.mb-6
              .flex
                .flex-shrink-0
                  svg.h-5.w-5.text-purple-400 viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                    path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"
                .ml-3
                  p.text-sm.text-purple-700
                    strong Community Fun Stuff:
                    |  The Baldrick community have created an amazing range of mounts and STLs that you can print and use today.

            .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.items-center
              div
                h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Medium Board Specifications
                ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                  li • 
                    strong Category:
                    |  Medium form factor
                  li • 
                    strong Board Footprint:
                    |  117mm × 74mm
                  li • 
                    strong Mounting Holes:
                    |  M3
                  li • 
                    strong Compatibility:
                    |  Matches similar boards in market
                  li • 
                    strong Typical Use:
                    |  Standard installations, existing mounts
              .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-4
                img src="/img/dimensions-medium.jpeg" alt="Medium Baldrick Board Dimensions" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
                p.text-sm.text-gray-600.mt-2.text-center Medium Baldrick Board Dimensions

          / Mounting Guidelines
          .bg-yellow-50.border-l-4.border-yellow-400.p-4.mb-8
            .flex
              .flex-shrink-0
                svg.h-5.w-5.text-yellow-400 viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                  path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"
              .ml-3
                p.text-sm.text-yellow-700
                  strong Important Warning:
                  |  Once again we ask 
                  strong DO NOT ENLARGE THE MOUNTING HOLES
                  | . Use the correct M3 hardware for secure mounting.

          h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Mounting Guidelines

          .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.mb-8
            .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-6.border.border-gray-200
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Hardware Requirements
              ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                li • 
                  strong Screw Size:
                  |  M3 (metric)
                li • 
                  strong Thread Pitch:
                  |  0.5mm
                li • 
                  strong Length:
                  |  6-8mm recommended
                li • 
                  strong Head Type:
                  |  Pan head or countersunk
                li • 
                  strong Material:
                  |  Stainless steel recommended
                li • 
                  strong Quantity:
                  |  4 screws per board

            .bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-6.border.border-gray-200
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Installation Tips
              ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                li • Use proper M3 hardware - do not substitute
                li • Ensure adequate clearance around the board
                li • Consider thermal management requirements
                li • Allow space for cable routing
                li • Test fit before final installation
                li • Use thread-locking compound if needed

          / Board Compatibility
          h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Board Compatibility

          .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6.mb-8
            .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-8
              div
                h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Small Form Factor
                ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                  li • BaldrickInput1
                  li • BaldrickSignals
                  li • Other compact controllers
                p.text-sm.text-gray-600.mt-3
                  | Perfect for space-constrained installations and hidden mounting applications.
              div
                h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Medium Form Factor
                ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                  li • Baldrick8
                  li • Baldrick17
                  li • BaldrickDMX
                  li • BaldrickSwitchy
                p.text-sm.text-gray-600.mt-3
                  | Standard size compatible with most existing mounting solutions and enclosures.

          / Enclosure Design Guidelines
          h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Enclosure Design Guidelines

          .space-y-6.mb-8
            .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Small Board Enclosures
              ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                li • Minimum internal dimensions: Add 10mm to board size
                li • Ventilation: Ensure adequate airflow
                li • Cable entry: Plan for power and data connections
                li • Mounting: Use M3 hardware with proper clearance
                li • Access: Consider maintenance and configuration access

            .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Medium Board Enclosures
              ul.space-y-2.text-gray-700
                li • Standard footprint: 117mm × 74mm
                li • Height clearance: Minimum 25mm recommended
                li • Thermal management: Consider heat dissipation
                li • Cable management: Plan for multiple connections
                li • Professional mounting: Compatible with standard racks

          / Related Fun Stuff
          h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Related Fun Stuff

          .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.mb-8
            .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 3D Printed Mounts
              p.text-gray-700.mb-4
                | Download community-created STL files for custom mounts and enclosures.
              = link_to fun_stuff_stls_and_mounts_path, class: "inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors" do
                | View STLs & Mounts

            .bg-white.border.border-gray-200.rounded-lg.p-6
              h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Technical Support
              p.text-gray-700.mb-4
                | Need help with mounting or enclosure design? Our support team can assist.
              = link_to support_path, class: "inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors" do
                | Contact Support

          .mt-8.bg-gray-50.rounded-lg.p-6.border.border-gray-200
            h4.text-lg.font-semibold.text-gray-900.mb-3 Community Designs
            p.text-gray-700.mb-4
              | The Baldrick community has created an amazing range of mounts, enclosures, and accessories. Check out our STLs & Mounts page to see what's available, or share your own designs with the community.
            = link_to fun_stuff_path, class: "inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors" do
              | View All Fun Stuff
